data.description: Embrace an exciting chance to settle into the Indian Creek community! This inviting  residence boasts a split floor plan, generously proportioned rooms, & an added bonus with a spacious family room. Laminate flooring graces most of the home, while plantation shutters add a touch of elegance. A new front door offers a fresh and stylish welcome. The sprawling back yard beckons, offering ample space for outdoor leisure and a salt water pool to enjoy! A thoughtfully designed kitchen & breakfast area, complete with pantry, & granite countertops stands as the heart of the home, connected to the two-car garage. Your personal haven awaits in the master bedroom suite, featuring a dressing area, walk-in closet, a dedicated vanity space & granite in bathrooms. Indian Creek delights in its low HOA fees, making it an even more appealing choice for your new home.
